          br
          p
            | Log in to Jobvite, click on <a href="javascript:popup3();" id="refer-a-friend"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/peOwDhE.png" height="30" width="120"></a>. 
            br 
            | Follow the instructions to submit the resume of the candidate you are referring.  
    section.container.guidelines
      .row
        .unit
          h2.referral-guideline-header
            | Referral Eligibility
          .list-section
            ul.qualification-list
              br
              li
                | To qualify for a referral bonus, you must submit your referral via Jobvite for a specific role.
              li
                | Referrals must be external candidates for full-time regular positions who we are not already in contact with. 
              li
                | Interns and contract roles are not eligible for referral bonuses.
              li
                | You cannot receive a referral bonus if you are in a recruiter within Talent Acquisition, will be part of the interview team or hiring decision to fill the role, in the managerial chain for the role, a contractor with RMS, or a VP level or above within RMS.   
              li
                | Referrals can only be accepted within the country in which you work.
              li
                | Ex-RMS employees are not eligible to be referred within 6 months of their leaving RMS.
